These are Puzzles for 2x3 Level 1

.:: Puzzle 2x3-Level-1-1::.
3 different games are played: go, snooker, scrabble
The people prefer 3 different types of sport: biathlon, rugby, surfing
1. the person who's sport is rugby is in the middle##1
2. the person playing scrabble is the person who's sport is surfing##1
3. the person playing go is on the far left##1

.:: Answer ::.
|            |      1      |   2    |    3    |
| Game   | go | snooker | scrabble   |
| Sport      | biathlon    | rugby  | surfing |

 #################################

 
.:: Puzzle 2x3-Level-1-2::.
The people have 3 different hobbies: collecting, traveling, puzzles
There are 3 different nationalities: argentine, canadian, nigerian
1. the argentine is on the left of the person who's hobby is puzzles##1
2. the canadian is on the far left##1
3. the canadian is the person who's hobby is traveling##1

.:: Answer ::.
|               |    1     |     2     |    3     |
| Hobby      | traveling | collecting     | puzzles      |
| Nationality   | canadian | argentine | nigerian |

 #################################

 
.:: Puzzle 2x3-Level-1-3::.
There are 3 different favourite beverages: soy-milk, tea, water
3 different pets are kept: rat, hamster, hedgehog
1. the person drinking tea is on the right of the owner of the hamster##1
2. the person drinking water is on the left of the owner of the hedgehog##1
3. the person drinking soy-milk is on the left of the owner of the hamster##1

.:: Answer ::.
|            |    1     |   2    |     3     |
| Beverage   | soy-milk | water  | tea       |
| Pet       | rat     | hamster | hedgehog |

 #################################

 
.:: Puzzle 2x3-Level-1-4::.
There 3 different types of food: pomegranate, radish, zucchini
The people prefer 3 different types of sport: water-polo, handball, rugby
1. the person eating radish is on the right of the person who's sport is rugby##1
2. the person eating pomegranate is on the right of the person who's sport is water-polo##1
3. the person who's sport is rugby is on the far left##1

.:: Answer ::.
|         |      1      |     2      |      3      |
| Food    | zucchini    | radish     | pomegranate |
| Sport   | rugby | water-polo | handball     |

 #################################

 
.:: Puzzle 2x3-Level-1-5::.
City: venice, nizza, colone
The people use 3 different means of transport: airplane, trike, van
1. the person driving the trike is the person traveling to colone##1
2. the person driving the trike is on the right of the person traveling to venice##1
3. the person traveling to colone is on the right of the person driving the airplane##1
4. the person traveling to venice is in the middle##1

.:: Answer ::.
|             |     1      |    2     |    3     |
| City         | nizza | venice     | colone |
| Transport   | van        | airplane | trike    |

 #################################

 
.:: Puzzle 2x3-Level-1-6::.
3 different games are played: monopoly, chess, scrabble
The people use 3 different means of transport: boat, motorbike, train
1. the person playing monopoly is on the right of the person driving the boat##1
2. the person playing chess is on the right of the person driving the motorbike##1
3. the person playing scrabble is the person driving the boat##1

.:: Answer ::.
|             |     1      |     2     |   3   |
| Game        | scrabble | monopoly      | chess  |
| Transport   | boat       | motorbike | train |

 #################################

 
.:: Puzzle 2x3-Level-1-7::.
The people prefer 3 different music-genres: jazz, r&b, salsa
The people prefer 3 different types of sport: rugby, rowing, handball
1. the fan of salsa is on the left of the fan of jazz##1
2. the fan of r&b is the person who's sport is rowing##1
3. the person who's sport is rugby is on the far left##1

.:: Answer ::.
|               |     1      |    2     |   3    |
| Music-Genre   | salsa      | jazz     | r&b    |
| Sport           | rugby | handball | rowing |

 #################################

 
.:: Puzzle 2x3-Level-1-8::.
There are 3 different nationalities: french, malaysian, indonesian
The people have 3 different hobbies: camping, card-games, skydiving
1. the person who's hobby is card-games is on the right of the french##1
2. the indonesian is on the left of the person who's hobby is skydiving##1
3. the malaysian is the person who's hobby is card-games##1

.:: Answer ::.
|         |      1      |     2     |     3      |
| Nationality    | indonesian | french | malaysian      |
| Hobby   | camping     | skydiving | card-games |

