1. the person traveling to nizza is the person who's hobby is filmmaking##1
2. the person traveling to san-francisco is on the far right##1
3. the person who's hobby is filmmaking is on the right of the person who's hobby is puzzles##1

.:: Answer ::.
|         |    1    |     2      |   3    |
| Hobby   | puzzles | filmmaking | chess  |
| City     | venice     | nizza      | san-francisco |

