.:: Puzzle 2x3-Level-1-10::.
House: futuristic, palace, colonial
The people perfer 3 different movie-genres: adventure, comedy, zombie
1. the person watching zombie movies is on the right of the palace house##1
2. the person watching zombie movies is on the far right##1
3. the person watching adventure movies is on the left of the colonial house##1

.:: Answer ::.
|               |   1    |     2     |   3    |
| House      | futuristic   | palace    | colonial    |
| Movie-Genre   | comedy | adventure | zombie |

