.:: Puzzle 2x3-Level-1-11::.
The people prefer 3 different music-genres: classical, punk, trance
There are 3 different favourite beverages: 7up, water, iced-tea
1. the fan of trance is the person drinking 7up##1
2. the person drinking 7up is on the left of the fan of punk##1
3. the person drinking iced-tea is on the far left##1

.:: Answer ::.
|               |     1     |    2     |   3   |
| Music-Genre   | classical | trance   | punk  |
| Beverage   | iced-tea    | 7up | water |

