.:: Puzzle 2x3-Level-1-13::.
The people use 3 different means of transport: helicopter, boat, jet-ski
The people have 3 different jobs:  dressmaker, journalist, social-worker
1. the journalist is on the right of the person driving the helicopter##1
2. the person driving the jet-ski is in the middle##1
3. the dressmaker is on the right of the person driving the jet-ski##1

.:: Answer ::.
|        |       1       |     2      |     3      |
| Transport   | helicopter     | jet-ski   | boat     |
| Job    | social-worker | journalist | dressmaker |

