.:: Puzzle 2x3-Level-1-14::.
The people have 3 different jobs:  coach, electrician, security-guard
House: farmhouse, art-deco, palace
1. the palace house is on the left of the security-guard##1
2. the security-guard is on the left of the electrician##1
3. the electrician is on the right of the farmhouse house##1

.:: Answer ::.
|       |    1     |       2        |      3      |
| Job   | coach    | security-guard | electrician |
| House   | palace | farmhouse     | art-deco        |

