.:: Puzzle 2x3-Level-1-15::.
The people perfer 3 different movie-genres: mystery, family, scientific
The people prefer 3 different music-genres: classical, funk, pop
1. the person watching family movies is on the far right##1
2. the fan of pop is on the left of the person watching family movies##1
3. the person watching scientific movies is on the right of the fan of funk##1

.:: Answer ::.
|               |  1   |   2   |     3     |
| Movie-Genre      | mystery  | scientific | family  |
| Music-Genre   | funk | pop   | classical |

 #################################

 
.:: Puzzle 2x3-Level-1-16::.
The people's birthday is in 3 different months: september, january, may
The people have 3 different jobs:  coach, lawyer, pilot
1. the lawyer is on the far right##1
2. the person who's birthday is in september is on the right of the person who's birthday is in january##1
3. the person who's birthday is in january is on the left of the pilot##1

.:: Answer ::.
|            |    1     |   2   |   3    |
| Birthday   | january | september | may    |
| Job        | coach    | pilot | lawyer |

 #################################

 
.:: Puzzle 2x3-Level-1-17::.
