.:: Puzzle 2x3-Level-1-18::.
There 3 different types of food: garlic, nectarine, papaya
The people use 3 different means of transport: snowmobile, train, boat
1. the person driving the boat is on the right of the person driving the snowmobile##1
2. the person eating garlic is the person driving the boat##1
3. the person eating papaya is on the right of the person eating nectarine##1

.:: Answer ::.
|         |     1     |    2     |       3       |
| Food    | nectarine | papaya   | garlic        |
| Transport   | train    | snowmobile | boat |

