.:: Puzzle 2x3-Level-1-19::.
The people have 3 different hobbies: camping, singing, sudoku
The people prefer 3 different types of sport: water-polo, skiing, cycling
1. the person who's sport is water-polo is on the left of the person who's sport is cycling##1
2. the person who's hobby is singing is the person who's sport is cycling##1
3. the person who's hobby is sudoku is on the right of the person who's hobby is singing##1

.:: Answer ::.
|               |    1    |    2    |   3    |
| Hobby         | camping | singing | sudoku |
| Sport   | water-polo | cycling     | skiing  |

