.:: Puzzle 2x3-Level-1-20::.
3 different brands of cigars are smoked: havana, dannemann, davidoff
The people prefer 3 different types of sport: cycling, snowboarding, soccer
1. the person who's sport is snowboarding is in the middle##1
2. the person who's sport is soccer is on the left of the havana-smoker##1
3. the dannemann-smoker is on the far right##1

.:: Answer ::.
|         |    1    |      2       |    3    |
| Cigar    | davidoff | havana       | dannemann  |
| Sport   | soccer  | snowboarding | cycling |

 